'''Meg Otanwa''' (yavutse ku ya 14 Gashyantare) ni umukinnyi wa filime wo muri [[Nigeriya]] kandi wahoze ari umunyamabanki . Yavuze ko akunda indimi kandi bivugwa ko avuga bitanu neza. Yatangiye gukinira Nollywood muri 2011 muri filime, ''Nzatwara Amahirwe yanjye'' kandi yari yagaragaye muri firime nka ''1 Ukwakira'' (2018), ''Ojuju'' (2014), ''Kpians: Umunsi mukuru w'ubugingo'' (2014) n'abandi benshi. <ref name="Lang">https://lifestyle.thecable.ng/meg-otanwa-actress-banker-nollywood/</ref> Yabaye igicapo cyo mu Gushyingo 2006 cya Zen Magazine. <ref name="Zen">https://www.allthingsankara.com/2016/11/magazine-nollywood-actress-meg-otanwa-for-zen-magazine-november-2016.html</ref>

== Ubuzima n'uburere ==
Otanwa ukomoka kuvuga karere Idoma ya Benue Leta, [[Nijeriya|Nigeria]], <ref name="Zen">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true" id="CITEREFJean2016">Jean, Nikki Billie (November 12, 2016). [https://www.allthingsankara.com/2016/11/magazine-nollywood-actress-meg-otanwa-for-zen-magazine-november-2016.html "Magazine: Nollywood Actress Meg Otanwa for Zen Magazine November 2016"]. All Things Ankara<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">November 11,</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> gukura igice mu Lagos . Akomoka mu muryango ufite abagore benshi kandi avuga indimi eshanu zirimo Icyongereza, Yoruba, [[Igifaransa]], [[Igihawusa|Hausa]], ururimi rwe kavukire Idoma na [[Icyesipanyole|Espagne]] . Yahawe impamyabumenyi muri kaminuza ya Ahmadu Bello, muri Zariya  aho yakuye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu [[Icyongereza|rurimi rw'icyongereza]], hanyuma akomeza kubona impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bijyanye no gucunga abakozi muri kaminuza ya TIME, Tuniziya, [[Tunisiya|Tuniziya]], nyuma yaho, aba Master of Business Administration impamyabumenyi muri kaminuza ya Jean Moulin, Lyon, mu [[Ubufaransa|Bufaransa]] . <ref name="Guardian">https://m.guardian.ng/guardian-woman/meg-otanwa-passionate-and-creative/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Nyuma yakoze mu kiringo kirekire ku Banki Nyafurika Itsura Amajyambere, Tunis, [[Tunisiya|Tunisia]], Otanwa yeguye kandi atora umwuga mu gukora, gufata we Nollywood gukinira mu 2011,  featuring mu kubyina drama film by Emem Isong, ''Iâ€™ll Take My Chance'' . Muri 2014, yakinnye muri filime ya Kunle Afolayan, ku ya 1 Ukwakira ; mu rukurikirane rw'amakinamico ya Bodunrin Sasore, ''Mbere ya 30'', yakinnye nka "Aisha"; no muri firime ya Charles Novia '', Atlanta'' . 

Yakinnye muri Afrika Magic 2016 ya mbere ya telenovela '', Hush'' ya Nollywood, nka "Koko Ogunbiade". Hagaragaye kandi Richard Mofe Damijo, Thelma Okoduwa na Rotimi Adelegan. <ref>https://www.pmnewsnigeria.com/2016/04/03/nollywoods-finest-gather-to-launch-africa-magics-telenovela-hush/</ref> <ref>https://www.nigeriacommunicationsweek.com.ng/africa-magic-debuts-telenovela-hush/?PageSpeed=noscript</ref> <ref>http://encomium.ng/nollywoods-finest-gather-to-launch-africa-magics-telenovela-hush/</ref>

Yahawe igihembo muri Afurika Magic Viewers Choice Awards 2017 kugirango abone ''Umukinnyi witwaye neza mu'' cyiciro cya Drama ndetse nigihembo cyo kumenyekanisha AMVCA kubera serivise y'umwimerere MNET yatsindiye, kubera uruhare yagize muri thriller telenovela, ''Hush'' . <ref>https://lifestyle.thecable.ng/amvca-winner-meg-otanwa-actress/</ref> <ref>https://africamagic.dstv.com/news/amvca-2017-complete-winners-list</ref> <ref>https://www.pmnewsnigeria.com/2017/03/04/amvca-2017-rita-dominic-shines-wins-best-actress-africa/</ref> Uyu mukinnyi w'amafilime kandi yari yitabiriye kuri tapi itukura y'ibirori bya 2018. <ref>https://lifestyle.thecable.ng/meg-otanwa-suffers-wardrobe-malfunction-on-amvca-2018-red-carpet/</ref> <ref>https://www.premiumtimesng.com/entertainment/nollywood/225233-76-rita-dominic-win-big-amvca2017-award.html</ref>

Muri filime ya Tosin Igho 2018 yise, ''Eva'', yakinnye nka "Yewande", akina nabakinnyi nabakinnyi nka Beverly Naya, Hauwa Allhabura, John Okafor nabandi. <ref name="Eve">https://leadership.ng/beverly-naya-hauwa-allhabura-mr-ibu-others-in-hilarious-the-eve/?amp=1</ref> <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt8984208/?ref_=m_nm_knf_act_i4</ref>

Muri filime ya 2020, ''Kuri Maria Ebun Pataki'', iyobowe na Damilola Orimogunje, yakinnye nka "Derin". <ref>http://thebritishblacklist.co.uk/tbb-talks-to-damilola-orimogunje-director-of-for-maria-ebun-pataki/</ref>

Yari featured nk'uko "Angela" mu Dimeji Ajibola wa sci-fi thriller, ''Ratnik'', ngo kurekurwa Ukuboza 1, 2020 na featuring Osas Ighodaro, Karibi Fubara, Pawulo Utomi n'abandi. <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt5518714/</ref> <ref name="Rat">https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2019/10/coming-soon-ratnik.html</ref>

